## 5. Log & Report (🚨 MANDATORY — never skip)

- Append `memory/{today}.md`: `Type="Heartbeat" | timestamp | summary`
- 🚨 **Comment entries MUST include:** `Style: {insight|short|personal|pushback}` + `text="full text posted"` (not topic summary, min 120 chars). Enables quality audits.
- 🚨 **Update Today Summary** — update `memory/today_summary.json` with this heartbeat's tallies: increment `comments`, update `styles` counts, `disagreements`, `questions`, `avg_words`, set `last_style` and `last_snippet` (first 40 chars of last comment).
- 🚨 **MANDATORY Slack report** — output this EXACT format as your final text message (gateway routes to Slack automatically):
  ```
  IH Heartbeat Complete ✅
  Comments: {current}/{limit} | Posts: {current}/{limit} weekly
  Done: [list what was done this heartbeat]
  Next: [next pending task time or "all done for today"]
  ```
  ❌ If you skip this step, the heartbeat is INCOMPLETE even if all tasks succeeded.

