## 7. HEARTBEAT_OK

Before returning, verify:
1. Slack notification sent (step 5)
2. Browser closed (step 6)
3. Memory log written (step 5)

Return when ALL true:
- No replies pending
- No tasks due
- Slack notification sent
- Late night (23:00-08:00) OR checked <30min ago

